Angel Prime/Icedragon/Rhinox



Angel Prime puts up a stasis field. he opens a com to Icedragon.




Angel Prime:

"put the vortex in the main core of the CF the power will raise the shields 
again."



Angel Prime lets down the stasis field and starts to fire fireballs at FZ.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Icedragon makes a mad dash toward the CF but one of the shots hit his left 
foot. he falls down but gets back up and starts to run. he freexe a small 
part of the shields of the CF and flicks it giving him a couple of seconds 
to get threw it. after that he runs and heads to the Main Core places the 
Vortex opener right inside and opens it. the vortex opener will keep under 
control while giving energy to the CF. [in another words like fire. if it is 
out of control it can destroy everything. but if you can control it can give 
you energy, warmth, etc.]  he heads towards the cloest panel and finds the 
location of the alliance members inside the CF and heads toward them.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Rhinox activates the internal autoguns and heads toward unitrons location.
